result.name: Glorious Cuisine

reviews.text:
Reasonable price and good quality and delicious food, 
This is high standard and delicious traditional Chinese food. The baby roast pig is amazing. Highly recommend to everyone who loves Chinese food.

Very hong Kong style restaurant. Every dishes are yummy.  The place is clean n the waiters are polite.  The most important is reasonable price.
Many old hk dishes can be found in there. E.g. deep fried fish intestines,  pepper soup.
food is good n reasonable price, suitable for group of ppl to go, quite a lot of hk-style signature dishes. However, not much staffs around to assist, need to be patient
I would say every dish is about average. The chicken was very well done and flavourful. It got to be too salty to the end as the chicken sat in the sauce for too long.

Foods ok
Prices fair
Place and restroom dirty extremely
Huge ratsssssss visit you all the time

reviews.text: 食物水準一流👍👍
好味👍

Reasonable price and good quality and delicious food, 
This is high standard and delicious traditional Chinese food. The baby roast pig is amazing. Highly recommend to everyone who loves Chinese food.
當夜點左沙窩魚頭煲，味道唔錯，但相信可以更好，因魚頭一早煎炸整好，後加工，其它的都滿意。
新鮮，好味，服務好，抵食！日本四大名蟹，鮮甜多肉多肉爆膏，新鮮生猛。 會推介畀朋友！
